        title: 'S-Corporation Formation', subtitle: 'Formaci√≥n S-Corp',
        description: 'Complete package: Articles of Incorporation + Bylaws + Initial Minutes + Banking Resolution + S-Corp Election Resolution. California Corporations Code ¬ß200‚Äì¬ß213.',
